title: Ruta Panamericana with Nike SB - Coming Soon
description:
Follow along with the Nike SB Ruta Panamericana tour. 
5 major cities, 10000 miles. 

Paul Rodriguez, Shane O'Neill, Theotis Beasley, Luan Oliveira, Karsten Kleppan, Ishod Wair, Youness Amrani.

October 4 - Sao Paulo, Brazil

October 8 - Lima, Peru
October 10 - Mexico DF
October 11 - Los Angeles, California
